description:
A DLC pack for GROOVE COASTER WAI WAI PARTY!!!! that includes 10 songs, navigators, and avatars!

This pack includes the following content.

■Song Pack (10 songs)
・Seizya no Kodo / Xeami
・Satisfiction / t+pazolite
・AM Kizoku Sutadontan Denka / IOSYS TRAX with Momiji Yamamoto
・Jukusei Jozo Hakkosei◎-Space Yogurt Earth- / MOSAIC.WAV
・The secrets of ghosts / SatoruAratani
・#AKKAN_BABY / MYUKKE.
・Adventure for Two Tones / Potwi
・Moonflare / aran
・Cryptocurrency Billionaire / void (Mournfinale)
・???(Secret)

■Navigator
・Sutadontan
・Kefir Koizumi
・Yume (Xmas) *with voice

■Avatar
・Sutadontan(2D)
・Kefir Koizumi(2D)
・Reindeer(3D)
・Swallowtail(3D)

*Some content will be unlocked via missions after downloading.
